node.text: I don’t really know where to start but I just want to say thank you. I really haven’t wrapped my head around 2,000,000 subscribers but I remember dreaming of an accomplishment like this every night as I went to bed when I started the channel. I used to get bullied online 6 years ago heavily for doing what I loved before it was “cool”. I’ve dedicated my life to doing what I truly love and never looked back and I’ve met the most amazing people along the way. There’s too many people to thank (y’all know who you are)but without my friends and family NONE of this would have been possible. You all have supported me and given me the life I always dreamed of. Thank you ❤️
